Some layers are referencing this layer.

en-US: Assign the Task to Compare with Data Source:
zh-TW: 指定資料來源的欄位用作訓練結果:

en-US: The project file should be in .json format
zh-TW: 專案的檔案應是 .json 格式的
對稱平均絕對百分比誤差(SMAPE)

en-US: Log Folder is where the training and testing results are saved. You can open the outputLogs folder generated in the start screen of Ladder to visualize the results.
zh-TW: 記錄資料夾是用來存放訓練記錄和測試結果的。您可以把裡面生成的 outputLogs 資料夾開啟至 Ladder 的開始畫面，以圖表方式顯示結果。

en-US: If you're using K-Fold validation, 1 round will be repeated for K epoches of data training. However, if you're using Repeated Random validation, 1 round will only go through 1 epoch of data training.
zh-TW: 若是你選了 K 次交叉驗證，1 圈驗證會進行 K 個完整資料集的訓練。但是當你選用重覆隨機驗證，1 圏驗證只會進行 1 次完整資料訓練。

en-US: Sample N items to trace and compare the predicted results during model training, where N≤30 is suggested.
zh-TW: 抽樣選取 N 個項目去瞭解跟比較在訓練過程的預測結果，建議 N≤30 。

en-US: Data sources available for data partitioning would be able to split standalone test or validation datasets. If not, cross validation would not be available, and the test set may be specified according to the data source type.
zh-TW: 可以分割的資料能讓你獨自建立測試/驗證資料集。否則，交叉驗證將不能使用，而測試資料集要視乎資料來源的定義。

en-US: Data type preprocessing allows enforcing a data type for its output. By default, it will be a float data (allowing decimal places). For classification tasks, you may need to use integers based on the discrete data characteristics.
zh-TW: 資料前處理可以強制模型導進資料的型態。在預設之下，資料會轉化成浮動值 (允許小數)。而分類項目，你需要轉換成整數，明確指示分類的離散性質。

en-US: A Regressor provides training on continuous target variables. The previous shape should be the same as the target variables. If not, a fully connected layer will be automatically added inside Ladder to transform the shape.
zh-TW: 迴歸可以提供針對連續性變數的訓練。如果前一層的形狀不等同目標項目的形狀，Ladder 會自動在裡面加入一個全連接層轉換形狀。

en-US: A Classifier provides training on categorical data. The target data supported by Ladder Classifier is one column of categorical values. If the last dimension of previous layer does not match the number of class, Ladder will automatically add a fully connected layer inside so as to compute the logit for each class. The prediction output will be a column of categorical data based on the argument-max of the logits.
zh-TW: 分類可以提供針對類別性變數的訓練。Ladder 分類任務需要一個欄位的類別資訊，該欄位中填寫不同類別的值。而如果前一層最後的維度不等同分類數量，Ladder 會在裡面自動加入一個全連結層，運算各類別的 logit 值，使得整個模型的預測資料輸出的一個欄位的分類值是基於各類別的 logit 值 argmax 而取得。

en-US: Model input sources must be converted to numbers before adding model layers. Try to use One-Hot Encoding.
zh-TW: 模型的輸進資料需要轉換成數字。請嘗試使用 One-Hot 轉換。

en-US: An open-source web app for editing basic neural network models and displaying the corresponding results, with the help of another open-source Python neural network training framework from our lab, Neural Simplycode.
zh-TW: 這是一個協助編輯基本類神經網絡架構及視覺化相關結果的開源網頁應用程式，及透過另一個我們實驗室的開源 Python 套件 Neural Simplycode 作為訓練類神經網絡模型。
